{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"My story begins right here actually in Rajasthan"},{"time":3000,"text":"about two years ago."},{"time":5000,"text":"I was in the desert, under the starry skies"},{"time":8000,"text":"with the Sufi singer Mukhtiar Ali."},{"time":10000,"text":"And we were in conversation"},{"time":12000,"text":"about how nothing had changed"},{"time":14000,"text":"since the time of the ancient Indian epic \"The Mahabharata.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":17000,"text":"So back in the day, when us Indians wanted to travel"},{"time":20000,"text":"we'd jump into a chariot and we'd zoom across the sky."},{"time":23000,"text":"Now we do the same with airplanes."},{"time":26000,"text":"Back then,"},{"time":28000,"text":"when Arjuna, the great Indian warrior prince,"},{"time":30000,"text":"when he was thirsty, he'd take out a bow,"},{"time":32000,"text":"he'd shoot it into the ground and water would come out."},{"time":35000,"text":"Now we do the same"},{"time":37000,"text":"with drills and machines."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39000,"text":"The conclusion that we came to"},{"time":41000,"text":"was that magic had been replaced"},{"time":43000,"text":"by machinery."},{"time":45000,"text":"And this made me really sad."},{"time":48000,"text":"I found myself becoming a little bit of a technophobe."},{"time":51000,"text":"I was terrified by this idea"},{"time":53000,"text":"that I would lose the ability"},{"time":55000,"text":"to enjoy and appreciate the sunset"},{"time":57000,"text":"without having my camera on me, without tweeting it to my friends."},{"time":60000,"text":"And it felt like technology"},{"time":62000,"text":"should enable magic, not kill it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64000,"text":"When I was a little girl,"},{"time":66000,"text":"my grandfather gave me his little silver pocket watch."},{"time":69000,"text":"And this piece of 50-year-old technology"},{"time":72000,"text":"became the most magical thing to me."},{"time":74000,"text":"It became a gilded gateway"},{"time":76000,"text":"into a world full of pirates and shipwrecks"},{"time":79000,"text":"and images in my imagination."},{"time":82000,"text":"So I felt like our cellphones"},{"time":84000,"text":"and our fancy watches and our cameras"},{"time":86000,"text":"had stopped us from dreaming."},{"time":88000,"text":"They stopped us from being inspired."},{"time":90000,"text":"And so I jumped in, I jumped into this world of technology,"},{"time":93000,"text":"to see how I could use it to enable magic"},{"time":95000,"text":"as opposed to kill it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97000,"text":"I've been illustrating books since I was 16."},{"time":99000,"text":"And so when I saw the iPad,"},{"time":101000,"text":"I saw it as a storytelling device"},{"time":103000,"text":"that could connect readers all over the world."},{"time":106000,"text":"It can know how we're holding it."},{"time":109000,"text":"It can know where we are."},{"time":111000,"text":"It brings together image and text"},{"time":113000,"text":"and animation and sound and touch."},{"time":116000,"text":"Storytelling is becoming"},{"time":118000,"text":"more and more multi-sensorial."},{"time":120000,"text":"But what are we doing with it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"So I'm actually just going to go in and launch Khoya,"},{"time":125000,"text":"an interactive app for the iPad."},{"time":129000,"text":"So it says, \"Place your fingers"},{"time":131000,"text":"upon each light.\""},{"time":133000,"text":"And so --"},{"time":136000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":160000,"text":"It says, \"This box belongs to ... \""},{"time":164000,"text":"And so I type in my name."},{"time":166000,"text":"And actually I become a character in the book."},{"time":168000,"text":"At various points, a little letter drops down to me --"},{"time":171000,"text":"and the iPad knows where you live because of GPS --"},{"time":174000,"text":"which is actually addressed to me."},{"time":176000,"text":"The child in me is really excited"},{"time":178000,"text":"by these kinds of possibilities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180000,"text":"Now I've been talking a lot about magic."},{"time":183000,"text":"And I don't mean wizards and dragons,"},{"time":186000,"text":"I mean the kind of childhood magic,"},{"time":188000,"text":"those ideas that we all harbored as children."},{"time":191000,"text":"This idea of fireflies in a jar, for some reason,"},{"time":193000,"text":"was always really exciting to me."},{"time":195000,"text":"And so over here you need to tilt your iPad,"},{"time":198000,"text":"take the fireflies out."},{"time":200000,"text":"And they actually illuminate your way through the rest of the book."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206000,"text":"Another idea that really fascinated me as a child"},{"time":209000,"text":"was that an entire galaxy could be contained"},{"time":211000,"text":"within a single marble."},{"time":213000,"text":"And so over here,"},{"time":215000,"text":"each book and each world"},{"time":217000,"text":"becomes a little marble"},{"time":219000,"text":"that I drag in"},{"time":221000,"text":"to this magical device within the device."},{"time":224000,"text":"And it opens up a map."},{"time":229000,"text":"All along, all fantasy books have always had maps,"},{"time":232000,"text":"but these maps have been static."},{"time":234000,"text":"This is a map that grows and glows"},{"time":237000,"text":"and becomes your navigation for the rest of the book."},{"time":239000,"text":"It reveals itself to you at certain points in the book as well."},{"time":242000,"text":"So I'm just going to enter in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"Another thing that's actually really important to me"},{"time":249000,"text":"is creating content that is Indian"},{"time":252000,"text":"and yet very contemporary."},{"time":254000,"text":"Over here, these are the Apsaras."},{"time":256000,"text":"So we've all heard about fairies and we've all heard about nymphs,"},{"time":259000,"text":"but how many people outside of India"},{"time":262000,"text":"know about their Indian counterparts, the Apsaras?"},{"time":265000,"text":"These poor Apsaras have been trapped inside Indra's chambers for thousands of years"},{"time":269000,"text":"in an old and musty book."},{"time":271000,"text":"And so we're bringing them back"},{"time":273000,"text":"in a contemporary story for children."},{"time":284000,"text":"And a story that actually deals with new issues"},{"time":287000,"text":"like the environmental crisis."},{"time":289000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"Speaking of the environmental crisis,"},{"time":314000,"text":"I think a big problem has been in the last 10 years"},{"time":317000,"text":"is that children have been locked inside their rooms,"},{"time":319000,"text":"glued to their PCs, they haven't been able to get out."},{"time":321000,"text":"But now with mobile technology,"},{"time":323000,"text":"we can actually take our children outside into the natural world"},{"time":326000,"text":"with their technology."},{"time":328000,"text":"One of the interactions in the book"},{"time":330000,"text":"is that you're sent off on this quest"},{"time":332000,"text":"where you need to go outside,"},{"time":334000,"text":"take out your camera on the iPad"},{"time":336000,"text":"and collect pictures of different natural objects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338000,"text":"When I was a child, I had multiple collections"},{"time":340000,"text":"of sticks and stones and pebbles and shells."},{"time":343000,"text":"And somehow kids don't do that anymore."},{"time":345000,"text":"So in bringing back this childhood ritual,"},{"time":347000,"text":"you need to go out"},{"time":349000,"text":"and, in one chapter, take a picture of a flower"},{"time":351000,"text":"and then tag it."},{"time":353000,"text":"In another chapter, you need to take a picture of a piece of bark"},{"time":355000,"text":"and then tag that."},{"time":357000,"text":"And what happens"},{"time":359000,"text":"is that you actually create a digital collection of photographs"},{"time":361000,"text":"that you can then put up online."},{"time":363000,"text":"A child in London puts up a picture of a fox"},{"time":365000,"text":"and says, \"Oh, I saw a fox today.\""},{"time":367000,"text":"A child in India says, \"I saw a monkey today.\""},{"time":369000,"text":"And it creates this kind of social network"},{"time":371000,"text":"around a collection of digital photographs"},{"time":373000,"text":"that you've actually taken."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375000,"text":"In the possibilities of linking together"},{"time":378000,"text":"magic, the earth and technology,"},{"time":381000,"text":"there are multiple possibilities."},{"time":383000,"text":"In the next book, we plan on having an interaction"},{"time":385000,"text":"where you take your iPad out with the video on"},{"time":387000,"text":"and through augmented reality,"},{"time":389000,"text":"you see this layer of animated pixies"},{"time":391000,"text":"appear on a houseplant that's outside your house."},{"time":395000,"text":"At one point, your screen is filled up with leaves."},{"time":398000,"text":"And so you need to make the sound of wind and blow them away"},{"time":401000,"text":"and read the rest of the book."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403000,"text":"We're moving, we're all moving here,"},{"time":406000,"text":"to a world where the forces of nature"},{"time":408000,"text":"come closer together to technology,"},{"time":410000,"text":"and magic and technology can come closer together."},{"time":413000,"text":"We're harnessing energy from the sun."},{"time":416000,"text":"We're bringing our children and ourselves"},{"time":419000,"text":"closer to the natural world"},{"time":421000,"text":"and that magic and joy"},{"time":423000,"text":"and childhood love that we had"},{"time":425000,"text":"through the simple medium of a story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}